snippet: Bill de Blasio may govern New York City, but he would not wow anyone with his feats of strength at the Prospect Park Y.M.C.A. in Brooklyn.
abstract: New York City Mayor Bill de Blasio will have to switch gyms when he moves from his Park Slope, Brooklyn, home to Gracie Mansion; de Blasio's exercise routine is remarkably light given that he is the most powerful elected official in the city.
lead_paragraph: Bill de Blasio may govern New York City, but he would not wow anyone with his feats of strength at the Prospect Park Y.M.C.A. in Brooklyn.

headline.main: A de Blasio Workout: New Routine, No Sweat
